author: Exo_brick
title: nice
review: I got this at Kmart for $3. It was a great set the pull back motor was  a great amusement when I was 6.I still play with it.I tweaked it so much that it can't be beaten by the new ones!If you find it, get it.

author: Yoda____
title: pull back fun
review: his set is a nice off roader and, like most other sets that have one, the pull back motor works well. I don't like the cable type things but the rest of the of the model looks good especially the colour scheme and the big wheels.
